## Priority Order for Demo Day
1. T-201 (LLM client) — everything depends on it
2. T-301, T-302 (parallel agents) — first handoff
3. T-303, T-304, T-305 (sequential agents) — proposal package
4. T-401 (orchestrator) — wires it all
5. T-501–T-507 (Flask routes) — makes it demoable
6. T-306, T-307 (twin + debrief) — step 2 and 3
7. T-601–T-606 (templates) — presentation layer
